snippet.title: Pikmin S Overview Trailer
snippet.description:
IMPORTANT: This video is outdated! This was made months prior to the Nintendo Fan Games Direct. This was made for F3, yet didnt see the light of day until months later.

This version of Pikmin S predates all Pikmin redesigns except for the Paint Pikmin.

PIKMIN S' ORIGINAL RELEASE WAS INCORRECT. IT NOW HAS AN UNDECIDED RELEASE DATE.
